text: László Csávás (born 19 September 1934) is a Hungarian ski jumper. He competed in the normal hill and large hill events at the 1964 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1934 births Category:Living people Category:Hungarian male ski jumpers Category:Olympic ski jumpers of Hungary Category:Ski jumpers at the 1964 Winter Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Budapest
